---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="About | AI-Enabled Growth Demo" description="About this Astro demo project and the developer behind it.">
  <Header title="About This Demo" subtitle="Built to showcase static-site engineering skills" />

  <main class="main">
    <section class="about">
      <div class="container">
        <article>
          <h2>Purpose</h2>
          <p>
            This project demonstrates proficiency in <strong>Astro</strong>, modern static-site architecture,
            and growth engineering best practices. It was built as a practical demonstration of skills
            relevant to high-velocity marketing web operations.
          </p>

          <h2>What's Included</h2>
          <ul>
            <li><strong>Reusable Components</strong> — Header, Footer, CTAButton, FeatureCard, LeadForm</li>
            <li><strong>Static-Site Generation</strong> — Pre-rendered pages with instant performance</li>
            <li><strong>Schema.org Markup</strong> — Structured data for AEO/GEO optimization</li>
            <li><strong>Lead Capture Forms</strong> — With hidden fields for campaign attribution</li>
            <li><strong>ABM Campaign Template</strong> — Personalized landing page structure</li>
            <li><strong>Responsive Design</strong> — Mobile-first CSS with modern layouts</li>
            <li><strong>Sitemap Generation</strong> — Automatic sitemap for SEO</li>
            <li><strong>Git-Based Workflow</strong> — Ready for CI/CD and team collaboration</li>
          </ul>

          <h2>Deployment</h2>
          <p>
            This project is configured for deployment on <strong>Vercel</strong> or <strong>Netlify</strong>.
            Zero-config deployment with automatic CI/CD on GitHub pushes.
          </p>

          <h2>About the Developer</h2>
          <p>
            25+ years of full-stack web development experience with expertise in static-site frameworks,
            marketing technology integrations, AI/ML, and high-velocity campaign execution.
            Based in Ontario, Canada.
          </p>
          <p>
            <a href="https://ojambo.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Ojambo.com</a> |
            <a href="https://github.com/ojambo" target="_blank" rel="noopener">GitHub</a> |
            <a href="https://linkedin.com/in/ojambo" target="_blank" rel="noopener">LinkedIn</a>
          </p>
        </article>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>

  <Footer />
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .main {
    min-height: 60vh;
  }
  .about {
    padding: 3rem 1rem;
  }
  .container {
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }
  article {
    background: white;
    padding: 2.5rem;
    border-radius: 8px;
    box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
  }
  h2 {
    color: #1a1a2e;
    margin-top: 2rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
    font-size: 1.5rem;
  }
  h2:first-child {
    margin-top: 0;
  }
  p {
    color: #555;
    line-height: 1.8;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }
  ul {
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    padding-left: 1.5rem;
  }
  li {
    color: #555;
    line-height: 1.8;
    margin-bottom: 0.25rem;
  }
  a {
    color: #4361ee;
    text-decoration: none;
  }
  a:hover {
    text-decoration: underline;
  }
</style>
